{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-page-js","path":"/resources/bitcoin-misconceptions/","result":{"data":{"resourcesJson":{"page":"/resources/bitcoin-misconceptions/","title":"Misconceptions","lead":"Clarifying Bitcoin misconceptions.","description":"You've probably heard Bitcoin described as being bad for the environment, or being used only by criminals. There are a lot of misconceptions around Bitcoin and the resourses below clarify many of these misconceptions.","body":null,"cardType":null,"lastUpdate":"06 February 2023","links":[{"title":"How Bitcoin is helping the environment","url":"https://www.cityam.com/why-i-think-bitcoin-could-be-a-key-to-saving-the-environment/","description":"Not many industries can take a potent greenhouse gas like methane and convert that into work that both secures a global network and drives down CO2. Bitcoin does this and more.","pills":[{"pill":"Read","color":"blue"}],"details":null,"image":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/1272eedc9675b13417499e7c6acbe19b/b8968/helpingenvironment.png","srcSet":"/static/1272eedc9675b13417499e7c6acbe19b/6fbd9/helpingenvironment.png 105w,\n/static/1272eedc9675b13417499e7c6acbe19b/88648/helpingenvironment.png 210w,\n/static/1272eedc9675b13417499e7c6acbe19b/b8968/helpingenvironment.png 420w,\n/static/1272eedc9675b13417499e7c6acbe19b/1a20b/helpingenvironment.png 840w","sizes":"(min-width: 420px) 420px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/1272eedc9675b13417499e7c6acbe19b/73ab7/helpingenvironment.webp 105w,\n/static/1272eedc9675b13417499e7c6acbe19b/b04e8/helpingenvironment.webp 210w,\n/static/1272eedc9675b13417499e7c6acbe19b/e1c45/helpingenvironment.webp 420w,\n/static/1272eedc9675b13417499e7c6acbe19b/cf69a/helpingenvironment.webp 840w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 420px) 420px, 100vw"}]},"width":420,"height":220}}}},{"title":"Bitcoin is Protecting Human Rights Around the World","url":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xLYYh4aPXAM","description":"&ldquo;It's an escape hatch from tyranny,&rdquo; writes the Human Rights Foundation's Alex Gladstein. &ldquo;It's nothing less than freedom money.&rdquo;","pills":[{"pill":"Video","color":"purple"}],"details":null,"image":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/f6158862f116e4b93a81bc087a3a705e/fb99e/humanrights.jpg","srcSet":"/static/f6158862f116e4b93a81bc087a3a705e/10661/humanrights.jpg 105w,\n/static/f6158862f116e4b93a81bc087a3a705e/11542/humanrights.jpg 210w,\n/static/f6158862f116e4b93a81bc087a3a705e/fb99e/humanrights.jpg 420w,\n/static/f6158862f116e4b93a81bc087a3a705e/fb762/humanrights.jpg 840w","sizes":"(min-width: 420px) 420px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/f6158862f116e4b93a81bc087a3a705e/73ab7/humanrights.webp 105w,\n/static/f6158862f116e4b93a81bc087a3a705e/b04e8/humanrights.webp 210w,\n/static/f6158862f116e4b93a81bc087a3a705e/e1c45/humanrights.webp 420w,\n/static/f6158862f116e4b93a81bc087a3a705e/cf69a/humanrights.webp 840w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 420px) 420px, 100vw"}]},"width":420,"height":220}}}},{"title":"Bitcoin is Not for Criminals","url":"https://unchained.com/blog/bitcoin-is-not-for-criminals/","description":"Just as the internet is not for drug dealers and terrorists, bitcoin is not for criminals. It is for everyone.","pills":[{"pill":"Audio","color":"green"},{"pill":"Read","color":"blue"}],"details":null,"image":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/2d6deb60af588c2bf8c854cf42e59080/b8968/unchained.png","srcSet":"/static/2d6deb60af588c2bf8c854cf42e59080/6fbd9/unchained.png 105w,\n/static/2d6deb60af588c2bf8c854cf42e59080/88648/unchained.png 210w,\n/static/2d6deb60af588c2bf8c854cf42e59080/b8968/unchained.png 420w,\n/static/2d6deb60af588c2bf8c854cf42e59080/1a20b/unchained.png 840w","sizes":"(min-width: 420px) 420px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/2d6deb60af588c2bf8c854cf